ActIndian Act
PrecisAcceptance of a BAND COUNCIL RESOLUTION wherein the CAMPBELL RIVER INDIAN BAND further amends a Surrender affecting its Reserve No. 11 in British Columbia, by withdrawing some 146 m² from the surrendered area in order to grant them to a band member as compensation for lands previously conveyed to the band by that same member.
